text: Kira Kazantsev (born July 20, 1991) is an American beauty pageant winner. She was crowned Miss America on September 14, 2014. Before that, she was Miss New York 2014. She works against domestic violence and abuse. "She’s trilingual! Kazantsev — a daughter of Russian immigrants — speaks Russian and Spanish in addition to English." Here are 10 things you need to know about Miss America Kira Kazantsev nydailynews.com Retrieved 13 March 2015 Kazantsev was born in San Francisco, California. ==References== Category:Miss America winners Category:People from San Francisco Category:1991 births Category:Living people
